{"type":"message","id":"937590e0","parentId":"56f58306","timestamp":"2026-03-24T03:33:21.076Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway 重启成功，现在向主人汇报切换结果，包括配置变更摘要和下一步需要确认的事项（OPENROUTER_API_KEY）。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **切换完成！**\n\n---\n\n## 🎉 模型已切换为小米大模型\n\n**配置变更：**\n1. ✅ 添加 openrouter 提供商\n2. ✅ 添加小米 MiMo V2 Pro 模型\n3. ✅ 设置为主模型（primary）\n4. ✅ Gateway 已重启\n\n**当前配置：**\n- **主模型：** `openrouter/xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro`\n- **备用模型：** `bailian/qwen3.5-plus`, `bailian/kimi-k2.5`\n\n**模型参数：**\n- 上下文窗口：256K tokens\n- 最大输出：65536 tokens\n- 支持：文本 + 图像输入\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ 需要配置 API Key\n\n小米模型通过 OpenRouter 接入，需要设置 `OPENROUTER_API_KEY` 环境变量。\n\n**设置方法：**\n```bash\n# Windows PowerShell\n$env:OPENROUTER_API_KEY=\"your-openrouter-api-key\"\n\n# 或者添加到系统环境变量（永久）\nsetx OPENROUTER_API_KEY \"your-openrouter-api-key\"\n```\n\n如果没有 API key，系统会自动回退到备用模型（通义千问）。\n\n---\n\n主人，我已经准备好用小米大模型继续 AI 帝国建设了！🚀\n\n下一步做什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774323194386}}
